Paolo Orsi","museum","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/097",{"slug":109,"type":106,"name":105,"uri":107,"description":110,"location":111},"097","An outstanding collection of archaeological material. The collection ranges from Siracusa and the surrounding territory (Megara Hyblaia, Akrai, Kasmenai etc) to encompass all of eastern Sicily, reaching as far as Gela and Agrigento. The ground floor covers prehistory through to the end of the Classical period. Upstairs includes Hellenistic and Roman Syracuse and a display of material from the catacombs. A gallery displaying material from Hellenistic eastern Sicily is in preparation.",{"settlement":76,"region":76,"country":112,"address":113,"geo":114},"Italy","Viale Teocrito 66, 96100 - Siracusa",{"lat":115,"lon":116},37.07636989,15.2866213,{"_":118,"type":119},"14603","inventory",{"_":121,"mainLang":122,"languages":123},"Ancient Greek","grc",[121],{"type":125,"bibl":126},"edition",[127,140,151],{"type":128,"n":129,"author":130,"date":131,"citedRange":132,"ptr":133,"ref":135,"inscriptionDate":131,"title":137,"citation":138,"uri":139,"year":131},"bulletin","NSA","Orsi","1895","511 no. 236",{"target":134},"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3T2DS245",{"_":136,"target":136},"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001711","Nuove esplorazioni nelle catacombe di S. Giovanni nel 1894","\u003Cspan>Paolo Orsi, «Nuove esplorazioni nelle catacombe di S. Giovanni nel 1894», \u003Ci>Notizie degli Scavi di Antichità\u003C/i>, 1895, 477–521\u003C/span>","https://www.zotero.org/groups/isicily/items/3T2DS245",{"author":141,"date":142,"citedRange":143,"ptr":144,"ref":146,"inscriptionDate":142,"title":148,"citation":149,"uri":150,"year":142},"Manganaro","1988","84",{"target":145},"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/RZSFKACR",{"_":147,"target":147},"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427","La Sicilia da Sesto Pompeo a Diocleziano","\u003Cspan>Giacomo Manganaro, «La Sicilia da Sesto Pompeo a Diocleziano», \u003Ci>Auf